Remarks
. This species is distinguished from its congeners by the combination of the following characters: 
1
) the rounded labrum; 
2
) the blunt teeth on left mandible; 
3
) emarginated posterior margin of abdominal sternite VIII; 
4
) slender and elongate parameres and apical broad sclerites of aedeagus.
